                        <summary>A horizontal scroll of calligraphy in the Xing Shu style, written by Chen Yuan (陳垣,1880-1971). The text is from the 夷夏篇第十六 section of the book titled 通鑒胡注表微, authored by Chen Yuan.</summary>
